node.text:
I’ve never been so happy to say goodbye to a year, 2020 was a rollercoaster for most of us👀
Some of the highest highs & lowest or lows for me, but we got through it & we are wiser & stronger than ever 💪🏼
First trip for the year, really hoping this year brings me many more travels than last year did 🤞🏼🤞🏼
@tonestudioapp

OVER THE MOOON 🌜

thank youuuu to everyone for encouraging us to never give up on this exemption, we got the news a week ago & liam jumped on the next flight to Sydney 😍 3rd time lucky 🤞🏼
#sydney #lovers #australia

node.text:
Back in australia 🇦🇺 and here’s a little wholesome week in my life 🥺🤍

when I left 15 months ago I honestly thought I’d be back a couple months later, it’s been a big year, and more than anything I’ve missed my family & friends, now that entering australia is a lot more chillll I’m happy to come back for an aussie festive summer !

Also how cuuuuute is my nephew 🤭

#australia #reunited #summer
